<div id=col20 >
    <table width=479px border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
    <p>
    <tr><td valign=top align=left>
    <span id=txt21 >
        <span class=textregion2>The Cannonballs Resurrection forums are now open! <a href="http://cannonballs.mybb3.org/">Click Here</a> to visit the forums.</span><br>
    </span>
    </td></tr>
    <tr><td valign=top align=left>
    <span id=txt22 >
        <span class=textregion2>Also, the About CB page and the new FAQ page is finally finished. The Links page has also been updated.</span><br>
    </span>
    </td></tr>
    </p>
    </table>
</div>
<div id=col23 >
    <table width=383px border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
