        <span class=textregion2>This website has been moved to Google’s new host because they are closing their old one.</span><br>
    </span>
    </td></tr>
    </p>
    </table>
</div>
<div id=col25 >
    <table width=409px border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
    <p>
    <tr><td valign=top align=left>
    <span id=txt26 >
        <span class=textregion2>Cannonballs Resurrection now has a Myspace Page! <a href="http://www.myspace.com/cannonballs_resurrection">Click Here</a> to see it.</span><br>
    </span>
    </td></tr>
    </p>
    </table>
</div>
<div id=col27 >
    <table width=337px border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
    <p>
    <tr><td valign=top align=left>
    <span id=txt28 >
        <span class=textregion2>CANNONBALLS PATCH RELEASED!</span><br>
    </span>
    </td></tr>
    </p>
    </table>
</div>
<div id=col29 >
    <table width=483px border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
    <p>
    <tr><td valign=top align=left>
    <span id=txt30 >
        <span class=textregion2>That’s right! I released a patch that will allow access to all islands! This is not a joke, get the patch <a href="http://resurrectcannonballs.googlepages.com/island.zip">Here</a>. Also find it in the downloads section! NOTE: Islands can be accessed only 1 at a time, so to access another island, simply close the game and apply the island patch of your choice, and reopen the game. All island patches are included in the download. Enjoy.</span><br>
    </span>
    </td></tr>
    </p>
    </table>
